{"title":"矿山诗情（二首）","authors":["孙友田"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山诗情（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙友田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是电车头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拉着一串煤车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从深深的地层下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向井口奔行……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿井下，巷道纵横，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前方亮起一盏绿灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦胧中给我清晰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹豫时给我坚定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谨慎，越过弯道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢，穿过险洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快些开过去吧”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到绿灯的叮咛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿井下，各种车辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都为我让道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们站在一旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羡慕我的轰轰隆隆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对身后的煤块说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那绿色的光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在召唤绿色的生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你回到明亮的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与太阳相会的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要感激我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要感激闪闪的绿灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接班的来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来一缕晨风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和晨风里那一句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清新的问候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋战了一夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与这里的一切暂时分手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再摸摸挺立的支柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再看看熟悉的电钮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快上井吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井上的太阳照红了新楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光，在你们矿工的床上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺好了温暖的被褥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，谁愿意去睡呢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗完澡又都精神抖擞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把眼圈的炭灰洗净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又都恢复了健美、俊秀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的去赏花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的去打球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的去逛街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的去访友……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有个小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要去火车站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要亲自迎接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次来矿探亲的女友……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}